snippet.title: Champion of Turnabouts [FT] All In, Collin-!
snippet.description:
[A Visual Novelty First-Time Playthrough]

Colin Faust is a down-on-his-luck gambler looking for the biggest fish out there in an attempt to turn his fortunes around - a rumored undefeated poker player named Phoenix Wright??

Let's shuffle up and deal???

Poker? In my Ace Attorney Online??
-----------------------------------------
Champion of Turnabouts, by TimeAxis!

Entry for The Miracle Happen ; ) Competition Hosted by Trybien and Spongesonic

Rumors in the underworld have been circulating about an undefeated Poker player who's never lost in seven years. Your mission, should you choose to accept it, is to put an end to that streak, and write the story of a new Poker legend.

Find it on Court Records here! https://aaonline.fr/forum/viewtopic.php?p=783014&hilit=Champion+of+Turnabouts#p783014
